trans-unit.source: The ServiceNameElement class represents a configuration element for a service name used in a <xref href="System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElementCollection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: A classe de ServiceNameElement representa um elemento de configuração para um nome de serviço utilizado um <xref href="System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElementCollection"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement"> </xref> classe.

trans-unit.source: When this constructor is used to initialize a new instance of the <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement> class, the <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement.Name%2A> property is set to `null`.
trans-unit.target: Quando este construtor é utilizado para inicializar uma nova instância do <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement>classe, o <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement.Name%2A>propriedade está definida como `null`.</xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement.Name%2A> </xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement.Name%2A> property should be set to an appropriate value for the application before calling the <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElementCollection.Add%2A> method to add the <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement> instance to the <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElementCollection> class.
trans-unit.target: A <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement.Name%2A>propriedade deve ser definida para um valor adequado para a aplicação antes de chamar o <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElementCollection.Add%2A>método para adicionar a <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement>instância de <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElementCollection>classe.</xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElementCollection> </xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement> </xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElementCollection.Add%2A> </xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement.Name%2A>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the Service Provider Name (SPN) for this <xref href="System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement"></xref> instance.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define o nome de fornecedor de serviço (SPN) para este <xref href="System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement"> </xref> instância.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> that contains the representation of SPN for this <xref href="System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement"></xref> instance.
trans-unit.target: A <xref:System.String>que contém a representação do SPN para este <xref href="System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement"> </xref> instância.</xref:System.String>
